HEADWORD: Ago
<hw>A*go"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a. & adv.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>ago</ets>, <ets>agon</ets>, p. p. of <ets>agon</ets> to go away,
